Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上有很多不可思议的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以甜点和甜点和甜点先生们就从天而降了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你在这儿干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神北同学…吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝…君?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是生活指导老师在模仿直枝君的声音之类的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有老师会那种特技啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲剧了 我出不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝君 拉我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食蚁兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…犰狳?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…神北同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概是因为你的裙子挂着哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 直枝君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食蚁兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那果然是食蚁兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娶不到新娘子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来就娶不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我就努力娶个女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当没被看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就万事OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 难得一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃个甜甜圈吧YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有茶喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的Best Place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果广为人知了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种层面上都会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你就是共犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学喜欢吃甜食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃甜点时会感觉很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这很微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因此就能感到幸福却是弥足珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以甜食很伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果直枝君觉得幸福我就会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人幸福时 自己多多少少也会感同身受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幸福时 我也幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幸福时 你也幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直循环下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能发现 幸福的螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能发自内心这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.32,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个理论的确会带给人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.31,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好直枝君来这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明同班却没说过话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我是来拉人入队的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们成立了一个草棒球队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※草棒球 即业余棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但队员不太够 所以我在拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4号三垒手是蒲公英吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草儿打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是草儿打棒球啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是在蓝天下悠闲地打棒球啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠闲地打…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓝天下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学怎么看都不像会打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子超——饿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开饭啦开饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁小气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.94,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你啦 别囔囔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们成立了一个棒球队—Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.58,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,本来错就在你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.48,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你抢了我的米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其成员除去谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有真人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.15,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肌肉需要碳水化合物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.19,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.05,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,还我!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.36,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,给我算了嘛 就当为我的肌肉做点贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早的闹什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是这个白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.61,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,说谁白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.21,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这四人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.14,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,叫个头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们组个乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐队名字就叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐队?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是棒球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 是棒球来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看乐队漫画被感动了所以有点情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实搞什么都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组棒球队果然只是心血来潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 还差5个队员来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧找齐然后为棒球挥洒青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意向不是棒球这种拐弯抹角的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是直接交手的热血战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冢原卜伝?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※冢原卜伝(1489-1571) 战国时代的剑圣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么放开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要打架吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人先发飙了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不吐槽直接应战了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 给我武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的武器是 肥皂!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人泡沫男!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥是肥皂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原真人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你一个光荣称号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人获得了「忘带脑子的男人」称号!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差5个队员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都升上高二了还有人会想打棒球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还需要5个这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你知道枣铃去哪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天她值日可黑板还没擦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又去找猫玩了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她眼里只有猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道她只在乎自己和猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 仗着自己受男生欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 五十六
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持 坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上第一次双足行走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然在这里啊 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 理树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你值日 怎么能跑出来玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好完成自己的职务会和同学越来越疏远的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和班上的女生关系也不怎么好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上有和你关系很好的女生?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐我后面的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫关系好?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没朋友对不起你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会因此死掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还有我们这些青梅竹马陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是以后毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还一直这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管闲事的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列侬如是说道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面好像写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:32.62,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界里存在着某种秘密 想知道就完成现在起我下达的所有任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界里…存在着某种秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密是指什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 还有一张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下达第一个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决男生宿舍仓库的卫生问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这信是谁写的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪写的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫哪里会写字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们偷偷跟踪列侬的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就能找着犯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这么做总觉得有点卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 你难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想挑战这任务?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要完成它就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是个骗小孩的恶作剧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是有人存心骚扰你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认犯人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个犯人试图告诉我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃的眼神里满是兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像猫会追逐眼前晃动的毛茸茸的东西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这个世界到底有着怎样的秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有的只是平淡无奇的日常生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说其中让我感到一丝不安的事物…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突发性急睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Narcolepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是我从小就患上的病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会导致突然失去意识陷入睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说起来 理树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备让你当4号击球手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当4号?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似最弱的理树逐渐成长为最强的4号击球手就是所谓的王道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么的王道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只有4名队员…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还谈什么4号击球手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我 这身 肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美吧 美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们 赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去解决男生宿舍仓库的卫生问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仓库就是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很龌龊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次大扫除恐怕是在明治维新的前夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要做啊 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把地方弄干净点我倒是没意见啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为啥我也得帮忙打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说 我是一想做扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚脐眼就会痒得要跳肌肉万岁舞星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 找着宝物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全系列都齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们刚要开始打扫啊 别乱放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为被招集对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草儿棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮上直枝君的忙我会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 你是说你愿意加入我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枣同学也是队员之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.11,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起努力打棒球吧 嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 铃超认生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 神北同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 铃 快道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 你是叫神北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何戴着连指手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打棒球要用到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 棒球中要用到的可不是你这种手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用到的…是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种也不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我成为队员之一前还有件事不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.27,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不放心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是打扫卫生这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此我也认了 就当练肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务 你要做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能打扫得这么干净
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想夸死自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃你要谢谢人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托了神北同学的福才完成了任务嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这下棒球社的活动室就收拾干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's 棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是棒球社的活动室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.37,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.72,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那丫头没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.88,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说问题有多大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眉间皱纹永驻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她本人倒是干劲十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只觉得她全身上下都是不安要素
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先进行入队测验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便判个不合格打发她走人麻烦事就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测验?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么第一问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为 打棒球需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…友情!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.39,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了 居然一不小心就被这少年漫似的正解感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测验通常不都是测运动能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了还有腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么首先进行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击球测验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 看不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我给你示范一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塑胶球棒很轻 这样应该没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我感觉问题很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来测跑垒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后测接球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是真正的棒球手套…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蒲公英先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很遗憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 最后一问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为打棒球需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有友情!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北小球 你具备了打棒球所需的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你入队了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起你就是我等Little Busters的队员了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才到底测了些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话叫我小球酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在认生?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多指教哦 铃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太难接受了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囧 吓跑她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:20:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是还不习惯这种交际 不知道该作何反应而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她还没被人这么叫过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这么说我就是肌肉酱囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得叫我肌肉酱哦 铃酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫起来很顺耳的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒绝不会很沮丧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沮丧啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人一直这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…裙子…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又开始这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这种快乐时光能一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密…是指什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一样 「那个」突然就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突发性急睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Narcolepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这个世界的联系被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…坠向了梦的深渊
